	* macros/gnome-libgtop-sysdeps.m4 (libgtop_postinstall): 
	Added `AC_SUBST(libgtop_postinstall)'. This is used in
	`src/daemon/Makefile.am' to make the server suid root or
	sgid kmem if required.

